  "key_strengths": [
    "Explicit translational milestones with validation thresholds prevent vague 'toward clinical application' language",
    "Route framing based on evidence level (association/mechanism/validation/clinical) ensures appropriate step sequencing",
    "Feasibility-sensitive route design aligns translational ambition with resource reality",
    "Prohibition on overstating translational readiness from basic or associative evidence is rigorously enforced"
